                    "action_type": {
                        "type": "stat_block_section",
                        "subtype": "action_type",
                        "name": "Two Actions"
                    },
                    "frequency": "three times per day",
                    "effect": "You breathe an elemental blast that deals 25d6 damage (DC 40 basic Reflex save) in either a 60-foot cone or a 100-foot line (your choice). The breath\u2019s damage type matches the Breath Weapon of the dragon type associated with the  *orb of dragonkind* (acid for the black orb, electricity for the blue orb, and so on).",
